						 <p>This in no way went where I thought it was, especially since I saw the title of the image at the start of the article. Overall, I love the heartwarming concept of it, and I loved the idea of someone just floating above the clouds, only to wake up and receive have a million dollars and the option for a gold plane! I needed something like this today, thank you!</p> 
